		[i:CalamityMod/HalibutCannon]:
		This fish can be researched.
		'''
	FishOnStudied:
		'''
		[i:CalamityMod/HalibutCannon]:
		This fish has been researched.
		'''
	FishByPuzzle:
		'''
		[i:CalamityMod/HalibutCannon]:
		This fish can be used as a puzzle piece.
		'''

	SkillSlot: {
		Hover1: Left Click: Select
		Hover2: Right Click: Pin
		Hover3: Scroll Wheel: Scroll
		Hover4: Hold: Drag
		Hover5: W Key: Store in Library
	}

	DomainUI: {
		TitleText: Abyssal Domain
		ExtraEyeTitleText: Tier X
		CrashedLabelText: System Crashed
		EyeDesc1:
			'''
			The first eye opens, tearing a rift in the dark side of your consciousness.
			You hear the sound of tides that shouldn't exist, as a clammy chill begins to seep through the veil of reality.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			'''
		EyeDesc2:
			'''
			The second eye overlaps with the first, and your vision blurs with unfocused double images.
			Reality blurs like a water-damaged photograph, as the dreary seascape of another dimension forces its way into the current space.
			A new domain has been forcibly opened within the original, forming a bizarre, dual-layered nested dimension.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			'''
		EyeDesc3:
			'''
			A tearing agony rips through your forehead as three spectral blue eyes, glowing with an ominous light, roll wildly beneath your skin.
			Light begins to be swallowed by this space, and the abyssal whispers from within your body no longer sound like hallucinations, but distinct chewing sounds.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			'''
		EyeDesc4:
			'''
			Four eyes split into two pairs, covering your own. The once-separate abyssal projections begin to overlap and fuse.
			The world in your eyes is no longer as it was; the structure of matter is deconstructed and reorganized within the murky seawater.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			'''
		EyeDesc5:
			'''
			Your skin becomes pale and bloated, like a corpse long submerged.
			Countless restless eyes swim and scramble beneath your skin like fish, finally converging on your forehead, tearing open a hideous singular eye.
			The five tiers of the domain completely merge, granting you the ability to twist causality within the distorted space.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] to restart yourself.
			'''
		EyeDesc6:
			'''
			The sixth eye opens upon your heart.
			It pumps no longer warm blood, but eerie black water, fetid and cold, like sewage soaked with rotting corpses.
			With every pulsation, it stirs visible dark blue veins within the sea.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] to restart yourself.
			'''
		EyeDesc7:
			'''
			Seven eyes arrange themselves in a bizarre array on your forehead, bursting with light to the pulse of time.
			The domain begins a frantic erosion of reality. Wherever its borders reach, matter dissolves like sand, and laws are rewritten by the tides.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] for a wide-area restart.
			Press [Halibut_Superposition] to use Superposition Strike.
			'''
		EyeDesc8:
			'''
			The eighth eye materializes as a silent vortex in the palm of your hand.
			The water pressure within the domain becomes almost palpable; light bends here, and sound dies here.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] for a wide-area restart.
			Press [Halibut_Superposition] to use Superposition Strike.
			'''
		EyeDesc9:
			'''
			Nine is the absolute number. Nine eyes form an illusory ring of the abyss above your head.
			The last trace of humanity has been washed away by the seawater. What stands here now is a shell bearing an endless sea of corpses.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] for a wide-area restart.
			Press [Halibut_Superposition] to use Superposition Strike.
			'''
		EyeDesc10:
			'''
			Tiers lose their meaning; one is infinity.
			You have become the abyss, and the abyss is you.
			Wherever your gaze falls is a new Genesis.
			You have reached the end of this shore and become the deity of the other.
			[Line]
			Press [Halibut_Domain] to open or close the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Teleport] to teleport within the domain.
			Press [Halibut_Clone] to let the past invade the present.
			Press [Halibut_Restart] for a wide-area restart.
			Press [Halibut_Superposition] to use Superposition Strike.
			Hold Left Click to initiate infinite superposition and infinite restart.
			'''
		LayerTitleFormat: Tier {0}
	}

	ResurrectionUI: {
		TitleText: Abyssal Resurrection Status
		LinePercentFormat: Percentage : {0:F1}%
		LineValueFormat: Resurrection Value : {0:F1} / {1:F1}
		LineRateFormat: Speed   : {0:F3}/s
		HeaderSummaryText: Current Situation Assessment
		RateLevelVeryLow: Dead Silence
		RateLevelLow: Whispers
		RateLevelMedium: Restless
		RateLevelHigh: Boiling
		RateLevelDanger: Breach
		Phase1: The resurrection is still calm, the abyss remains silent.
		Phase2: Non-existent sounds of tides can be heard; extremities begin to feel cold.
		Phase3: Hallucinations intensify. The heavy pressure of the deep sea begins to press on the eyes and heart.
		Phase4: The logic of reality begins to collapse; your existence is being rewritten by something terrifying and cold.
		Phase5: The critical point has broken. Humanity is dissipating; you are about to become part of that sea of corpses.
		Trend1: Almost Stagnant
		Trend2: Slow Leakage
		Trend3: Continuous Surging
		Trend4: Violent Infusion
		Trend5: Instantaneous Collapse
		SummaryFormat: Current Diagnosis: {0} [Erosion Trend: {1}]
	}

