			Press [W] on a skill to store it.
			'''
		HintAddToList: "[W] Add to List"
		HintRemoveFromList: "[W] Store in Library"
	}
}

MuraText: {
	Subtest_Text0: We must head to the Underworld to unleash the powers of light and dark. It will trigger a warp storm, but it must be done, recruit, to pen a magnificent stroke for our crusade!
	Subtest_Text1:
		'''
		I miss the fiery tempering of the Brimstone Crags. Let's go meet its guardian.
		I can feel two gazes upon us. Go take care of them.
		'''
	Subtest_Text2:
		'''
		A prison within the True Ice bulwark. A powerful psyker is held there. Free him; he will be a great asset in reclaiming Terra.
		A decisive battle is approaching. Those heaps of scrap metal plan to unite in a vain attempt to stop us.
		Tell them with blade and blood that the march of our crusade will crush all xenos heresy and abominable intelligence.
		'''
	World_Text0: Previously Upgraded World: <{0}> | Recorded Level: <{1}>
	Subtest_Text4: In the jungle, someone's former clumsy creation still wanders. As a failure, it should rightfully be just a pile of scrap metal.
	Subtest_Text5: A shell of interwoven flesh, the resentful wraith of an ancient battlefield, a ceaselessly destructive golem. It destroys all things, and we shall destroy it.
	Subtest_Text6: The star gods of old have long fallen. What remains is but a mere maggot. Let us put an end to the era of the star gods once and for all.
	Subtest_Text7: Let that aggregation of souls in the dungeon wither beneath my blade. Its soul will be the finest nourishment.
	Subtest_Text8: A pathetic deity lingering by siphoning solar thermal energy. Its heretical fire must be completely extinguished.
	Subtest_Text9: That alien plant deep in the jungle. Go tear its petals, crush its bulbs, and let its sap stain this land.
	Subtest_Text10: That witch who threw herself into chaos has a deformed clone sister. Kill that xeno, and offer its blood and fire to the blade.
}

