MurasamaTrialQuestLine: {
	QuestCategory: Demon Blade Murasama · Trials
	TrackerWaiting: Target is absent, awaiting summons...
	TrackerFighting: "{0}: {1:0%}"
	Trial_0: Desert Phantom
	Trial_1: Sand Sea Hunt
	Trial_2: Invader
	Trial_3: Corruption Purge
	Trial_4: Parasitic Threat
	Trial_5: Gelatinous Defiler
	Trial_6: Dungeon Breach
	Trial_7: Path to the Underworld
	Trial_8: Tundra Shackles
	Trial_9: Abyssal Cleansing
	Trial_10: Brimstone Purging Flame
	Trial_11: Steel Gears
	Trial_12: Twin Eye Annihilation
	Trial_13: Mechanical King Skull
	Trial_14: Calamity Shadow Operation
	Trial_15: Jungle Blossom
	Trial_16: Petrified Frontline
	Trial_17: Plague Eradication
	Trial_18: Golem Breaker
	Trial_19: Astral Termination
	Trial_20: Lunar Fall
	Trial_21: Phantom Sanction
	Trial_22: Wraith Exorcism
	Trial_23: God-Slaying Serpent
	Trial_24: Jungle Flame
	Trial_25: Core Termination
	Trial_26: Chaos Judgment
	Trial_27: Primordial Return
	TrialSummary_0: Prove yourself to me, recruit.\nThat slimy blue blob is a good place to start.\nHandle it.
	TrialSummary_1: The siren remnants beneath the sand sea still roam.\nTrack it down and end it.
	TrialSummary_2: The moon hangs high in the night. Let's go burst that giant eyeball flying around up there, and make that false god permanently blind.
	TrialSummary_3:
		'''
		The remnants of false gods taint the lands of Terra. Go liberate the corrupted continents.
		Hack that false god's brain to pieces, chop up that purple worm!
		I want to see your blade dance through xenos flesh!
		'''
	TrialSummary_4: The corrupted earth still throbs like a heart. The flesh parasites are still active; the corrupted tumors are still thinking. Go banish them entirely!
	TrialSummary_5: Do you feel it? That foul corruption reeking of gel.\nPurify this filthy aggregate completely.
	TrialSummary_6:
		'''
		The curse at the dungeon entrance has loosened. I feel psychic energy stirring in its depths, mixed with screams, wails, whispers...
		Shatter that giant skull.
		'''
	TrialSummary_7: Step into the Underworld. That wall of flesh spanning the lava—that is our door to the next era.\nTear it apart.
	TrialSummary_8: In the bitter cold of the northern reaches lies a sealed creation of ice and snow.\nCrush it before it can fully unseal.
	TrialSummary_9: The outcast of the Sulphurous Sea blocks our quest for the treasures of the abyss. Go end its devouring and wandering.
	TrialSummary_10: The heretical fire of that Brimstone Emissary deep in the lava is an eyesore. Go extinguish it.
	TrialSummary_11: A massive steel worm stands in the way of our crusade. Chop it into pieces.
	TrialSummary_12: Those mechanical eyes look down on us—pierce them with your blade.
	TrialSummary_13: The skeleton lord donned steel armor thinking it could stop us? Shatter that metal skull.
	TrialSummary_14: That witch who threw herself into chaos has a deformed clone sister. Kill that xeno, and offer its blood and fire to the blade.
	TrialSummary_15: The mad plant deep in the jungle has gone berserk. Use your blade to end this out-of-control growth.
	TrialSummary_16: The foolish Lihzahrd race only knows how to worship these stubborn stones. Let's smash it to dust and destroy their faith.
	TrialSummary_17: Amidst the steam and toxic gas is a bee-machine hybrid. Shoot that filthy thing down.
	TrialSummary_18: That golem of destruction is rampaging across the land. Pulverize its steel body completely.
	TrialSummary_19: The astral worms are gathering cosmic energy here. End it, so this star field can be ours.
	TrialSummary_20:
		'''
		That false god hiding on the dark side of the moon is nothing but a flawed patchwork.
		Go sever its tentacles, rip out its heart, and drink deep of its blood.
		'''
	TrialSummary_21: A pathetic deity lingering by siphoning solar thermal energy. Its heretical fire must be completely extinguished.
	TrialSummary_22: The aggregate of undead deep in the dungeon. Let those restless souls finally be silenced.
	TrialSummary_23: That arrogant cosmic serpent is stirring behind the veil of the world. End his ambitions.
	TrialSummary_24:
		'''
		The Jungle Dragon, the last auric draconic descendant of Terra. It is vastly different from other xenos and deserves our respect.
		However, right now we need it to die once more to strip it of its Auric Soul.
		These materials will be used to forge an incredibly superior set of gear.
		'''
	TrialSummary_25:
		'''
		That heretic of the mechanical church firmly believes his Exo Mechs surpass the power of gods.
		Such a belief is utterly absurd. Let us return those Titans to their natural state—a pile of scrap metal.
		'''
	TrialSummary_26:
		'''
		A witch who once possessed outstanding psychic talent, who should have been a great asset in defending Terra, but who has long since lost herself to chaos.
		We can only banish her. Plunge the blade into her chest, and let the fire of loyalty burn away her rotting soul.
		'''
	TrialSummary_27:
		'''
		Our path of conquest is already unstoppable. Shatter the armor of the demonic dragon beneath the black abyss.
		Use the Terminus and engage in the final decisive battle with the xeno.
		'''
}

SHPCTrialQuestLine: {
	QuestCategory: SHPC · Trials
	TrackerWaiting: Target is absent, awaiting summons...
	TrackerFighting: "{0}: {1:0%}"
	Trial_0: Ocular Autopsy
	Trial_1: Corruption Sample
	Trial_2: Source of Parasitism
	Trial_3: God of Gel
	Trial_4: Seal Breakthrough
	Trial_5: Deep Sea Contamination
	Trial_6: Brimstone Sampling
	Trial_7: Mechanical Worm
	Trial_8: Twin Eye Dismantlement
	Trial_9: Steel Skull
	Trial_10: Calamity Clone
	Trial_11: Ecological Survey
	Trial_12: Ancient Tech
	Trial_13: Interstellar Coordinates
	Trial_14: Secrets of the Lunar Dark Side
	Trial_15: Core Expedition
	Trial_16: Wraith Observation
	Trial_17: Devourer of Gods
	Trial_18: Feather of the Draconic Descendant
	Trial_19: A Visit to the Creator
	Trial_20: Witch Audit
	Trial_21: Battle of Terminus
	TrialSummary_0:
		'''
		Master, the first trial target is that hovering giant eye.
		Please defeat it. I need to collect complete data on its anti-gravity mechanisms.
		'''
	TrialSummary_1:
		'''
		The giant worms in the corrupted earth and the fleshy brains are high-quality biological samples.
		Master, please sever their core tissues. I must analyze the propagation mechanism of this ecological erosion.
		'''
	TrialSummary_2:
		'''
		The brain of corruption and the fleshy aggregate are infectious sources with a hive mind.
		Master, please eliminate them. Their coordinated parasitic patterns have been added to the collection list.
		'''
	TrialSummary_3:
		'''
		The gelatinous aggregate—a god-level target with no central nervous system or fixed form.
		Master, please shatter its core. I will properly record this chaotic architecture.
		'''
	TrialSummary_4:
		'''
		A wall of flesh spans the depths of the Underworld; it is a seal from a bygone era.
		Master, please blast through it. This is a necessary breakthrough towards a new era.
		'''
	TrialSummary_5:
		'''
		The giant worm of the Sulphurous Sea has surfaced.
		Master, please dismantle its devouring organs. I need to confirm how this pollution source operates.
		'''
	TrialSummary_6:
		'''
		The Brimstone Emissary deep within the lava is diffusing a high-heat reaction.
		Master, please extinguish its core flame. I will simultaneously record its energy conversion efficiency.
		'''
	TrialSummary_7:
		'''
		The first mechanical target is a giant steel worm.
		Master, please slice it into recyclable scrap. Try to keep the drive structure intact.
		'''
	TrialSummary_8:
		'''
		The second mechanical target is that pair of mirrored eyeballs. Coordinated combat is their primary feature.
		Master, please dismantle their weapon modules one by one, and be mindful of their laser's scorch radius.
		'''
	TrialSummary_9:
		'''
		The final mechanical target wears the skull of an old king.
		Master, please crush it. Once this mechanical invasion protocol is shut down, I will conduct a concluding analysis.
		'''
	TrialSummary_10:
		'''
		That witch's clone is roaming around. Though it's only a replica of necromancy,
		it is sufficient to calibrate my reaction model for calamity. Master, please destroy it.
		'''
	TrialSummary_11:
		'''
		Several alluring large bulbs have bloomed underground in the jungle.
		Master, please accompany me to see them. I need to gather some experimental data.
		'''
	TrialSummary_12:
		'''
		The ancient automaton deep in the temple awaits a power-up sequence to activate.
		Master, please take me to visit it. Reverse-engineering ancient tech might prove useful.
		'''
	TrialSummary_13:
		'''
		That group of fanatical cultists at the dungeon entrance is performing some ancient ritual, attempting to block information from the heavens.
		Master, please interrupt them. I need those hidden interstellar coordinates.
		'''
	TrialSummary_14:
		'''
		The secrets of the dark side of the moon will be known to us.
		Master, this might set certain things back on track.
		'''
	TrialSummary_15:
		'''
		The deity parasitic in the planet's core has noticed us.
		Master, please go to the Underworld and take a look. Her method of utilizing thermal energy is worth recording.
		'''
	TrialSummary_16:
		'''
		The wraiths of the dungeon are amalgamating into a massive symbiote.
		Master, the hive consciousness of this ectoplasmic architecture is quite rare. Please take me to observe it.
		'''
	TrialSummary_17:
		'''
		It is not a carbon-based lifeform; it can tear the dimensional membrane with its physical body alone.
		It devours gods, but we are not gods. Defeat it, and let this be recorded in the logs.
		'''
	TrialSummary_18:
		'''
		The only surviving draconic descendant in the world; its very existence is a miracle.
		Master, please take me to see it. I need to collect a sample of its feathers.
		'''
	TrialSummary_19:
		'''
		It is time to meet my former creator.
		Master, please retrieve the control core of the Exo Mechs.
		'''
	TrialSummary_20:
		'''
		That witch has been conducting chaotic experiments. We have enough data.
		Master, please terminate her operations. This farce must end.
		'''
	TrialSummary_21:
		'''
		Master, the enemies you previously defeated have formed a coalition and are preparing a final assault.
		Please be prepared. I will monitor the battlefield throughout and assist you in settling this once and for all.
		'''
}

